data.name: cbxJaeryoGubun.UserSQL
data.value: -- JAERYO_GUBUN SELECT B.CODE , B.CODE_NAME FROM INV0102 B , INV0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.CODE_TYPE = 'JAERYO_GUBUN' -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = A.CODE_TYPE ORDER BY B.SORT_KEY

data.name: xEditGridCell19.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '','なし' FROM DUAL UNION SELECT B.CODE , B.CODE_NAME FROM BAS0102 B , BAS0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.CODE_TYPE = 'SUBUL_CONV_CODE' -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = A.CODE_TYPE ORDER BY 1

data.name: grdOcsChk.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.JAERYO_CODE ,A.JAERYO_NAME ,A.CHK3 DRG_PACK_YN ,A.CHK2 PHAMARCY_YN ,A.CHK1 POWDER_YN ,A.TOIJANG_YN HUBAL_CHANGE_YN ,A.BUNRYU2 MAYAK_YN ,A.SMALL_CODE ,B.CODE_NAME1 SMALL_CODE_NAME ,A.CAUTION_CODE ,D.CAUTION_NAME ,C.START_DATE ,E.DANUI SUNAB_DANUI ,E.DANUI_NAME SUNAB_DANUI_NAME ,A.SUBUL_DANUI SUBUL_DANUI ,F.CODE_NAME AS SUBUL_DANUI_NAME ,A.STOCK_YN STOCK_YN ,A.SUBUL_DANGA SUBUL_DANGA ,A.SUBUL_QCODE_OUT ,(SELECT Y.CODE_NAME FROM BAS0102 Y , BAS0101 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = 'K01' AND X.CODE_TYPE = 'SUBUL_CONV_CODE' -- AND Y.HOSP_CODE = X.HOSP_CODE AND Y.CODE_TYPE = X.CODE_TYPE AND Y.CODE = A.SUBUL_QCODE_OUT ) SUBUL_QCODE_OUT_NAME ,A.SUBUL_QCODE_INP ,(SELECT Y.CODE_NAME FROM BAS0102 Y , BAS0101 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = 'K01' AND X.CODE_TYPE = 'SUBUL_CONV_CODE' -- AND Y.HOSP_CODE = X.HOSP_CODE AND Y.CODE_TYPE = X.CODE_TYPE AND Y.CODE = A.SUBUL_QCODE_INP ) SUBUL_QCODE_INP_NAME FROM (SELECT X.SG_CODE , X.SG_UNION , X.SG_NAME , X.BULYONG_YMD , X.DANUI , Y.CODE_NAME AS DANUI_NAME , X.HUBAL_DRG_YN , X.HOSP_CODE FROM BAS0310 X , OCS0132 Y WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = 'K01' AND X.SG_YMD = ( SELECT MAX(Z.SG_YMD) FROM BAS0310 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = X.HOSP_CODE AND Z.SG_CODE = X.SG_CODE AND Z.SG_YMD <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) AND Y.HOSP_CODE = X.HOSP_CODE AND Y.CODE_TYPE = 'ORD_DANUI' AND Y.CODE = X.DANUI ) E , OCS0132 F , DRG0130 D , OCS0103 C , DRG0141 B , INV0110 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.JAERYO_CODE LIKE :f_jaeryo_code||'%' AND A.JAERYO_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_jaeryo_name||'%' AND NVL(A.SMALL_CODE,'%') LIKE :f_pre_small_code||'%' AND NVL(A.SMALL_CODE,'%') LIKE :f_small_code||'%' AND NVL(A.CHK3,'%') LIKE :f_drg_pack_yn||'%' AND NVL(A.CHK2,'%') LIKE :f_phamarcy_yn||'%' AND NVL(A.CHK1,'%') LIKE :f_powder_yn||'%' AND NVL(A.TOIJANG_YN,'%') LIKE :f_hubal_yn||'%' AND NVL(A.BUNRYU2,'0') LIKE decode(:f_mayak_yn,'1','1','%')||'%' AND NVL(A.STOCK_YN,'N') LIKE :f_stock_yn||'%' -- AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = A.JAERYO_CODE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN C.START_DATE AND C.END_DATE AND NVL(C.BEFORE_USE_YN,'N') LIKE :f_before_use_yn||'%' AND NVL(C.WONNAE_DRG_YN,'N') LIKE :f_wonnae_drg_yn||'%' -- AND B.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE1(+) = A.SMALL_CODE -- AND D.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.CAUTION_CODE(+) = A.CAUTION_CODE -- AND E.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.SG_CODE(+) = A.JAERYO_CODE -- AND F.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'ORD_DANUI' AND F.CODE(+) = A.SUBUL_DANUI ORDER BY A.JAERYO_NAME

data.name: grdOCS0108.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.ORD_DANUI , A.SEQ , A.CHANGE_QTY1 SUNAB_GIJUN , A.CHANGE_QTY2 SUBUL_GIJUN , A.HOSP_CODE , A.HANGMOG_START_DATE , B.CODE_NAME || '/' || FN_OCS_LOAD_SUNAB_DANUI_NAME(A.HANGMOG_CODE, A.HANGMOG_START_DATE) , B.CODE_NAME || '/' || FN_OCS_LOAD_SUBUL_DANUI_NAME(A.HANGMOG_CODE, A.HANGMOG_START_DATE) FROM OCS0108 A , OCS0132 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_aHangmogCode AND A.HANGMOG_START_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_aHangmogStartdate,'YYYY/MM/DD') AND B.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE(+) = A.ORD_DANUI AND B.CODE_TYPE = 'ORD_DANUI' ORDER BY A.HANGMOG_CODE, A.SEQ
